title: Transylbabies
description: A mission to babysit Snowmanpire babies in Transylbiria leads Vambre and Prohyas to attack the local monster townsfolk in misguided attempts to keep the Snowbabies safe.

title: Hurricane Chata
description: When V & V discover that Chata's emotions control the water in the lake, they use it to their advantage and start their own wave pool business.

title: Flush Hour
description: The babies learn the purpose of toilets.

title: Falafel's in Jail
description: Falafel's in trouble with the law despite pleading his innocence. Apple and Onion vow to break him out.

title: Planet X
description: When Rad returns to his home planet, he learns a shocking truth about alien society.

title: Guardian of the Unikingdom
description: Hawkodile insists the Unikingdom is more dangerous than it looks and sets out to prove it by taking his friends on bodyguard patrol.

title: Bearz II Men
description: The Baby Bears help a teenager accomplish his dream of being a famous singer.

title: Doug Out
description: Steven and Connie join Connie's father on a stake out.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: In Dreams
description: Steven's dreams start broadcasting onto his bedroom TV.

title: Joyride
description: At a rummage sale with Uncle Andrew, Axel and Zoe must stop Madcap from turning her long-lost tank toy, Joyride, into an agent of mayhem!

title: Franken Pelea
description: Ben se sube al Rustbuggy para recibir una lección de conducción a lo largo de las dunas de Cabo Cod. Pero el plan da un extraño giro cuando el Rustbuggy se transforma en un monstruo motorizado por Bootleg, otra transformación alienígena de Kevin 11.

title: Yo soy Polar
description: Cuando Polar se golpea la cabeza, Pardo y Panda se dan cuenta de que su comportamiento cambia.

title: O Mother, Where Art Thou?
description: Ma Vreedle threatens to blow up the sun if Ben and the Plumbers don't find her missing son!

title: Flyaway
description: When Adorabat's spirit transcends her body during a meditation exercise, Mao Mao and Badgerclops have to figure out a way to return her to the real world.

title: El Patron de Oro
description: Llega el Día de San Patricio y, luego de desear convertirse en un duende, Chico Bestia se obsesiona con el oro.

title: Appreciation Day
description: By trying to change Benson's opinion of them, Mordecai and Rigby accidentally create lots of work for themselves.

title: Three Cheers for Cheer
description: When hard-working Cheer exhausts her crew running a string of drills to protect a Whiffle orchard from possible emergencies, Share's belly badge accidentally creates two Cheer duplicates. Cheer takes a recreation break, unaware that her clones are working Share and the crew - who think they're the real Cheer - even harder.

title: Suerte
description: When Vic cheats on an enchanted board game, the malevolent characters come to life, and it's up to V & V to figure out how to put them back in the game.

title: Bucketboy!
description: When the girls tell Barry he's a hero, he takes it too far.

title: Cowbar Jones: Origines
description: Pardo presenta la precuela de su película de Crowbar Jones a Nom Nom, con la esperanza de que acepte actuar en la película.

title: The Scratch Pack
description: Axel and the team must run damage control after a loose spark of Minergy accidentally turns Zoe's old toys - a set of cute squishy kittens - into a pack of snarling beasts.

title: Beast Boy's St. Patrick's Day Luck, and It's Bad
description: The Titans (except Beast Boy) are cursed on St. Patrick's Day and must travel to the end of the rainbow for the cure.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: The Money
description: The Wattersons have run out of money and are torn between being broke and selling out. Richard has lost all of the family's money. Nicole is happy for the Wattersons to appear in a Joyful Burger commercial for some much needed cash. However Gumball protests as he is convinced it's selling out. He persuades the family to stick to their principles, but they find sticking to a tiny budget even harder.

title: Motel
description: Following an insect mishap Clarence's house needs to be fumigated forcing Mary, Chad, and Clarence into a motel. In the meantime, Clarence and Chad learn a bit about responsibility while Mary contemplates a life of letting go.

title: Sunken Treasure
description: A relaxing beach day becomes an underwater adventure when Unikitty and her friends find a message in a bottle.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: Don't Read the Comments
description: An obsession with comments and criticisms about him on the Board of Opinions drives Prohyas nuts, affecting Warrior missions for the worse and raising Vambre's ire, I mean, concerns.

title: Superstar Dan/Awesome Brawlers on Vacation
description: Superstar Dan: The Awesome Brawler's head to Tokyo for the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo Edition. While Wynton, Shun, Lia and Lightning see the sites, and enjoy the tastes of Japan, Dan, as the Los Volmos Champion, has official Bakugan Battle League duties and obligations that keep him busy./Awesome Brawlers on Vacation: Lia, Lightning, Shun and Wynton explore the sights of Toyko when a rogue Bakugan shows up and rampages. The Awesome Brawlers have to spring into action, rolling out their Bakugan to stop the rogue enemy before any real damage can be done.

title: Sarge esta a Cargo
description: Axel y el equipo deben rescatar a Sarge Charge de una misión en solitario en el patio trasero, que Orangutank ha convertido en su propio corazón personal de oscuridad.

title: El Favorito de la Profesora
description: Los ositos van a la escuela para escapar de sus vidas agitadas.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: Sarge in Charge
description: Axel and the team must rescue Sarge Charge from a solo mission in the backyard, which Orangutank has turned into his own personal heart of darkness.

title: Caillou Goes Shopping/Caillou Goes Apple Picking/Caillou's Halloween Costume
description: Caillou's crayons are all worn down or broken, so Mommy suggests a trip to the store for some new ones./Caillou's playschool is on a special field trip to an apple orchard./Halloween is coming and it's time to pick out a costume to wear.

title: Loteria
description: Cuando Vic hace trampa en un juego de mesa encantado, los malvados personajes cobran vida, y V y V son los responsables de averiguar cómo volver a ponerlos en el juego.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Cual Reloj?
description: Cuando una batalla con Kevin queda interrumpida, Ben se concentra en ser mejor que Gwen en el Campamento Espacial. Pero cuando Kevin regresa con la mirada extrañamente puesta en su prima, nuestro héroe debe descubrir quién está realmente detrás de todo esto: iCharmcaster!

title: #WhySoBlue
description: Supergirl must rein in a reckless new hero, the Blue Beetle.

title: One Step Forward, Two Steps Back
description: When the ninja learn that the only way to acquire the second Key-tana is by winning a dangerous race in Terra Technica they'll have to find some racing cars in unexpected ways.

title: Meet Cheetara
description: Cheetara is the coolest cat around! Not only is she so fast that she can outrun lightning, but so clever she can outsmart Mumm-Ra's evil plans! Villains don't stand a chance against Cheetara…well, unless Mumm-Ra uses his Doom Staff, then she might be in trouble.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: Pocoyo Gets it Right
description: Pocoyo wants to play 'pitch and putt' like his friends, Pocoyo and Elly, but he can't quite get the hang of it. He watches carefully and finally grasps where he was going wrong.

title: Cloris
description: When Clarence befriends an aging woman at the local retirement home, he's determined to remind her of her old self in order to convert the grumpy granny to his fun loving ways.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: Elephants!/Caillou and the Sheep/Caillou and the Puppies/The Duck Family/Clementine's New Pet
description: When Mom, Rosie and Caillou go to the zoo, Caillou can't wait to see the elephants./Grandma takes Caillou on a special visit to a sheep farm./Caillou and Dad go over to Mr. Hinkle's house to help him build a dog house./While Caillou and his family are on a picnic at the park, his beach ball accidentally rolls into a pond./When Mom takes Caillou to Clementine's to see her new pet, she won't tell Caillou what kind of animal it is.

title: Cat Burglar
description: An alarmingly familiar cat burglar terrorizes Townsville.

title: Let's Go Camping!
description: A camping trip is planned - but Pocoyo and Pato have too much luggage. In the end they realize that all you really need for a nice camping trip are your friends - and then it doesn't really matter whether you're at home or away.

title: Flying/Dr. Lucas is in the House/Arlo's Portrait
description: After watching Findley in flight, Lucas wonders what it would be like to fly./ Dr. Lucas tries to make all his friends feel better but ends up under the weather himself./ Lucas decides to paint a portrait of Arlo. But Arlo can't sit still.

title: Parallel Paradox
description: Elliott finds himself having to be in two places at once.

title: I Strain
description: Petunia gets hooked on watching television and stops playing with her friends.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Study Time
description: Lion-O never pays attention during Tygra's training sessions so when he's asked to do a pop quiz on "sword magic" he accidentally opens a portal to the Astral Plane and releases the Nether Witch! The Witch imprisons Lion-O and Tygra in her nightmare realm and it's gonna take a lot of studying to figure out a way home. Wonder if the Astral Plane has any great teachers lying around.

title: Meet Lion-O
description: Meet Lion-O and the Thundercats! After fleeing their home planet, the Thundercats find themselves stranded on Third Earth where they face the evil Mumm-Ra. But Lion-O is strong! He's tough! There's nothing he can't do! Except maybe open really big jars of cookies…

title: Crack the Whip
description: Amethyst is left in charge of Steven and Connie, and there will be no training while she's around!

title: Hustlecup
description: When Buttercup loses the Professor's latest invention, she'll have to beat The Gangreen Gang at their own game to get it back.

title: Elly's Big Chase
description: Elly inadvertently sets off on a fantastic journey - all the while fast asleep on her chair - as Pocoyo and Pato protect her from danger.

title: Cast Aside the Truth
description: Hawkodile breaks his arm in a careless spill and lies to his friends about the accident to keep from looking bad.

title: Gem Hunt
description: Steven and Connie track a Gem monster through the wilderness but its tracks lead them to mystery.

title: El Desnudo de Mao Mao
description: Cuando Mao Mao pierde la ropa mientras intenta escalar el Rubí Puro Corazón, tiene que regresar al cuartel general antes de que amanezca.

title: Savage Axel
description: Bearbarian helps Axel get in touch with his wild side as Orangutank "liberates" nature from an apartment building - tossing potted plants of all sizes out the window and onto innocent bystanders below!

title: Nocaut
description: Axel y el equipo hacen malabarismos sin despertar al tío Andrew de su siesta y evitar que Orangutank robe el último invento de Andrew: ila Caja Knockout!

title: The Other Fight
description: Eliminated from the Bakugan Battle League, Ajit is airlifted by drone to a massive cargo ship in the middle of Tokyo Bay. Now that he's on board the cargo ship, he must rescue Dan and Drago, and stop whoever is sabotaging the Battle League. Dan and Ajit investigate the mysterious cargo ship that the eliminated brawlers and Bakugan are being held on. Dan races to track down Drago, but along the way runs into a familiar face.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: El club de los solitarios
description: En lugar de celebrar el Día de San Valentín, Vic y Val se atreven a explorar una mansión encantada con sus rivales, Charlene y Piña.

title: Dressing Up
description: Bing and Coco are dressing up and they both need a crown. What will they do when they see there is only one crown?

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: Peeps
description: Benson gets surveillance cameras to keep track of Mordecai and Rigby on the job.

title: The Babysitter
description: Vic & Val want to sneak out to a secret fireworks show but are thwarted when their new babysitter, Xochi, outsmarts them at every turn.

title: VIP Baby You Know Me
description: Shag Rugg makes a VIP section in his family's Café to live his baller life style.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: ThunderSlobs
description: Tygra's feeling unappreciated by the other ThunderCats so he starts hanging out with Mumm-Ra and cleaning his Black Pyramid?! Whaaaaaaat?

title: Working Grrrl
description: Cheetara is the fastest living person in the universe until Monkian beats her in a race?! Now Cheetara has to find something else to be the best at and the rest of the ThunderCats have to find out how Monkian got so darn fast!

title: Beat Your Greens/Down N' Dirty
description: Beat Your Greens: When Broccoli Aliens from space invade Townsville, it's up to the Powerpuff Girls and all the children of Townsville to take a bite out of crime. Down N' Dirty: When Buttercup refuses to take a bath, the town kicks her out. But Buttercup decides to stick with her stink until her favorite thing is taken away from her.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Appleoni
description: The wrong person is getting credit for a new dance craze.

title: Suelta
description: Cuando el espíritu de Adorabat trasciende su cuerpo durante un ejercicio de meditación, Mao Mao y Colosal tienen que descubrir un modo de devolverla al mundo real.

title: Presentando a Kevin 11
description: En un encuentro de intercambio local, Ben se interesa en un coleccionable de Luchadores de Sumo. Pero cuando Kevin se apodera del objeto, nuestro héroe debe superar el arma secreta de Kevin para recuperarlo: iun 11º extraterrestre!

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Them's Fightin' Words!
description: After enjoying some local corn, Team Tennyson discovers a Hartfield-McJoy reenactment in the cornfield next door, but when Hex resurrects the ghosts of the real feuding families, Ben must find a way to bring them together if he is to save the day!

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Chip's Damage
description: Elodie enlists KO to help figure out what to do about Chip Damage.

title: The Fly
description: Apple and Onion must rid their apartment of a fly or face eviction.

title: Twisted Sister/Cover Up
description: Twisted Sister: The girls decide they need some help fighting crime so they create another Powerpuff Girl. But they don't get the combination of sugar, spice and everything nice quite right./Cover Up: Blossom and Bubbles learn that Buttercup has secretly been rubbing a security blanket before every battle to make herself a super fighter. Can the girls convince Buttercup that her strength is within?

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Cleaning Day
description: Victor & Valentino gain a newfound respect for cleanliness after Chata's house traps them inside its labyrinth of ancient, magical walls.

title: Better Than You
description: The Squashinator challenges Craig to a battle he can't refuse.

title: Whatever Happened to... Rippy Roo?
description: Rippy Roo visits the plaza.

title: Bismuto Casual
description: Perla invita a Bismuto a la pista de patinaje para darle una lección sobre cómo forjar relaciones humanas.

title: Balloon
description: Bing, Sula and Flop find a balloon stuck in a tree and play the Stuckie Duckie game. Will Bing and Sula remember to stick together?

title: Huracan Chata
description: Cuando V y V descubren que las emociones de Chata controlan el agua del lago, deciden sacar ventaja y comienzan su propio negocio de piscinas de olas.

title: Shun and Lightning/Premonition of a Storm
description: Shun and Lightning: Shun and Lightning are on the hunt for a rare Tumpee, when they run into McQ! With all the devices related crimes happening in Los Volmos, Shun decides to investigate to try to get to the bottom of McQ's nefarious dealings./Premonition of a Storm: After a run in with McQ, Shun and Lightning find themselves in a little bit trouble. They're trapped!  Tied up with no Bakugan to help them escape, and no one knows their whereabouts. It will take some big help to help them get out of this mess.

title: Field Trip
description: A group of teenage superheroes are being shown around the Fortress of Solitude when they inadvertently cause the phantom zone projector to trap Superman and release three Kryptonian criminals.

title: Mud Is Thicker Than Water
description: Ben, Gwen and Cousin Lucy try to find out how Psyphon's thugs are getting Plumber technology.

title: El Otro Lado
description: Axel debe "salvar" a Bobbie Blobby después de que ella se dañe al equipo de Madcap, tentado por Porcupunk y su afirmación de que ella pertenece a los juguetes malos.

title: Hearts
description: Bing and Sula choose their favourite things around the house and stickie them with hearts. What will happen when Sula gets to Bing's bedroom first?

title: The Joke is on Thomas
description: When Thomas and Percy's plan to surprise Diesel goes awry, the two friends still manage to cheer up Diesel... just not in the way they expected!
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: For a Few Brains More
description: Ben, Rook and Max must stop Ultimate Albedo from absorbing Azmuth's intelligence and taking over the galaxy.

title: River of Gold
description: Apple and Onion find a mysterious book but they better read it fast before it disappears forever.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Secret in a Bottle
description: Craig needs to get a secret off his chest, so he pays a visit to the Keeper of Secrets in the Creek.

title: The Lonely Haunts Club
description: Instead of celebrating Valentine's Day, Vic & Val take on a dare to explore a haunted mansion with their rivals, Charlene & Pineapple.

title: The Cave of Gelatinous Doom!
description: The Warriors don't have a worthy adventure to use their impressive new skull-and-crossbones-emblazoned Bonehead Magisword until they are sent on a quest to battle a mighty slime beast in the Dungeon of Gelatinous Doom!

title: Morituri Te Salutamus
description: Finn and Jake are trapped in the arena of the Fight King and must face gladiators to set themselves free.

title: Un Paso Adelante, Dos Pasos Atras
description: La única manera de que los Ninjas obtengan segunda Keytana es ganando una carrera en Tierra Technica y tiene que conseguir autos de carreras para eso.

title: Franken-Fight
description: Ben hops into the Rustbuggy for a driving lesson along the sand dunes of Cape Cod, but he takes a freaky switchback turn when the Rustbuggy is mutated into a motor-monster by Bootleg, another alien transformation of Kevin 11, with powers similar to Upgrade!

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Disappearing Carrots/Caillou Marches On/Who's Mooing/Follow That Sound!/The Music Box!
description: When a white rabbit eats a bunch of carrots set aside for a picnic lunch, Caillou and Rosie go looking him./When Caillou visits Clementine, he is impressed to see Billy practicing on a tuba./Caillou and his family are leaving for a picnic in the country but the ride feels very long for Caillou./On a winter evening, a strange sound grabs Caillou's attention./Caillou goes up to the attic with Mom and finds a box containing a teddy bear and a music box.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Los Gatos Rascadores
description: Axel y el equipo deben ejecutar el control de daños después de que una chispa suelta de Minergy accidentalmente convierta los viejos juguetes de Zoe, un conjunto de lindos gatitos blandos, en una manada de bestias gruñendo.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: The Monster
description: Lumpy Space Princess's parents have come to ask Finn and Jake to find their daughter and convince her to come home.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: Fright Wig
description: When the King cannot overcome his fears, he abuses having the Sheriff's Dept. on call.

title: It's Time
description: Mordecai and Rigby get in a fight over Margaret, and Mordecai sends them traveling through time by destroying all the clocks.

title: Peluca de Terror
description: Cuando el rey no logra superar sus miedos, se abusa de la ventaja que le da tener al departamento del sheriff de guardia.

title: I, Butler
description: The Bears use a robot bear to help around the house. But things get tricky when they lose control of the robot.

title: Lost and Found
description: When Thomas helps Nia make a delivery to the beach in Norramby, he insists he knows a shortcut and leads the way! But it turns out his memory isn't as good as he… remembered.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: #MotherKnowsBest
description: Hippolyta visits town and Diana is desperate to win her approval. But when Hippolyta unexpectedly takes a shine to Kara, Diana must curb her envy before they all get hurt.

title: Teacher's Pet
description: The Baby Bears escape their hectic lives by attending school.

title: Rio de Oro
description: Manzana y Cebolla intentan terminar un cuento antes de que el libro desaparezca para siempre.

title: Knockout
description: Axel and the team juggle not waking Uncle Andrew from his nap and stopping Orangutank from stealing Andrew's latest invention: the Knockout Box!

title: Piloto Siete
description: Mientras los Ninjas se preparan para la carrera Cinco Billones por Hora, Lloyd conoce a la Piloto Siete quien puede tener la clave de la victoria.

title: Osos Musicales
description: Los Osos bebé ayudan a un adolescente a cumplir su sueño de convertirse en un cantante famoso.

title: Pocoyo, Pocoyo
description: Pocoyo discovers a fabulous new playmate - his echoooo-ooo-ooo-ooo!

title: Yo Mayordomo
description: Los Osos usan un oso robótico que los ayuda con las tareas domésticas. Pero las cosas se complican cuando pierden el control del robot.

title: Benwolf
description: In New Mexico, Max stops to visit an old friend, who's a Navajo Chief. Suddenly, a powerful storm comes out of nowhere. And behind bolts of purple lightning, a Navajo werewolf appears. As Ben battles the werewolf, he appears to be bitten and turns into Benwolf.

title: Body Trouble
description: When Uncle Grandpa and Belly Bag have a disagreement, they separate and try to make each other jealous.

title: The Ultimate Heist
description: Albedo seeks a device that will finally change him back into his Galvan form; meanwhile, Ben is locked in Plumber HQ prison.

title: The K.O. Trap
description: KO, Rad, and Enid are caught in an especially devious trap.

title: La ninera
description: Vic y Val quieren colarse en un espectáculo secreto de fuegos artificiales, pero su plan se ve frustrado cuando su nueva niñera, Xochi, los supera en todo momento.

title: Coins/Canoe Trip/The Bulldozer/The Firefighter/The Timekeeper
description: Caillou accompanies Mom to the grocery store./When Caillou, Grandpa and Daddy go on a canoe trip, Caillou gets to see some wild animals./On an autumn day, Caillou and his Mommy take a walk and pass by a construction site./When Dad's burning toasts trigger the fire alarm, he decides it is the perfect opportunity to practice a fire drill./Caillou and his Mommy are finishing preparing a picnic lunch.

title: The Second Stage Begins/Mechanoids Attack!
description: The Second Stage Begins: With half of the brawlers eliminated, the second stage of the Bakugan Battle league begins. This round will be a timed race to the finish, with all kinds of tricks and traps that will slow down even the best brawlers./Mechanoids Attack!: Mechanoids have crashed the second stage of the Bakugan Battle League, causing all kinds of havoc. The Awesome Brawlers will now have to race against the clock, battling competitors and mechanoids if they want to make it through this round.

title: The Man
description: It's Granny Jojo's Birthday and she's brought an unexpected guest to dinner. Granny Jojo has brought a boyfriend to her birthday meal and Dad isn't happy about it. He bans Granny JoJo from ever seeing Louis again. When the kids get caught sneaking Granny Jojo out of the house, Dad challenges Louis to a man-off to prove once and for all who is the man of the house?!!

title: Juggling Balls
description: Pocoyo is very impressed with Elly and Octopus' trick of juggling. He wants to play too. Octopus makes Pocoyo practice lots of different activities but Pocoyo can't see the point because they aren't related to juggling… or so he thinks. In the end Pocoyo becomes the star of the show!

title: Custody Battle/City of Nutsville
description: Custody Battle: Mojo discovers the Rowdyruff Boys are back and is determined to show them that he is a more evil dad than Him./The City of Nutsville: The squirrels of Townsville are chirping mad! But when Bubbles loses her ability to speak a squirrel, the girls don't know how to calm the rodents down.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: The Music Store Thief
description: Instruments have been going missing from Apple and Onion's favourite music store and Chicken Nugget (who's in charge of security) doesn't want them hanging around and getting in the way.

title: Crisis en la roca de Ancianos
description: Una tragedia azota al Arroyo cuando los Ancianos quedan atrapados bajo la Roca Anciana. Ahora Craig, Kelsey y JP deben rescatarlos.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Beautopia
description: Susan Strong returns to tell Finn and Jake that her world is in danger!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: Something for Sula
description: Bing is making a picture for Sula with all of her favourite things on. Will Bing make Sula the perfect picture?

title: Squideo Games
description: When Vambre and Prohyas are hired for separate gigs, they end up having to battle each other to claim a rare Squideo from Lake Sprite in Galacton.

title: La super moto
description: Duncan hace que Beth crea que rompió su bicicleta impulsada a batería y hace que lo lleve de un lugar a otro en su carrito todo el día como castigo.

title: Uncle Grandpa Land
description: Pizza Steve must find a way to sneak onto his own roller coaster at the newly opened Uncle Grandpa Land.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Meet Mumm-ra and the Mutants
description: The Thundercats have met their match with the evil, undead Mumm-ra! He and the bumbling Mutants have made it their goal to stop the Thundercats by any means necessary, but of course the Thundercats have other plans!

title: Eyes on the Surprise
description: Every time Mush-Mush has tried to surprise his friend with a gift, Chep has always found out what it was. But Chep promises that this time he won't. And Lilit, who is too honest to keep a secret, promises she won't let Chep know what the surprise is. Both of them find this so hard! But Mush-Mush is one step ahead of them…

title: Cactus Makes Perfect
description: Cody's friends become concerned when he forms a new friendship with a cactus.

title: I'm the Sauce
description: Stuck inside because of bad weather, the Titans play rainy day games after Robin convinces them that indoor activities will cheer up the clouds and make the rain stop.

title: Problematic Prophecies
description: Elliott and Mo make a new friend, Nara, who has a very special ability.

title: Virtual Reality Bites
description: When the school switches to virtual reality, Harold uses the opportunity to get the respect he feels he rightfully deserves.

title: Sofa Cama
description: Cuando los Piratas del Cielo se infiltran en el cuartel general del sheriff, iponen en peligro a los héroes!

title: The Authority
description: Granny JoJo's overprotective behavior puts the Wattersons in danger...from themselves.

title: Ello Gov'nor
description: After watching a scary movie about a British Taxi, the guys have to help Rigby overcome his fears.

title: Knack
description: Bing, Sula and Pando are in the garden trying to find out what everyone's knack is. Will Bing find his own knack?

title: Baost in Show
description: When Bao Bao returns, and the King makes him his pet, Mao Mao must rescue his ex-partner.

title: The Cliffs of Hysteria
description: While being chased by Unagami's dreaded Red Visors the ninja must climb the 'Cliffs of Hysteria', however, they make a startling discovery: Unagami is converting players into energy cubes in order to build a portal into the real world!

title: En Suenos
description: Los sueños de Steven comienzan a transmitirse en el televisor de su dormitorio.

title: Mushroomates
description: When ants invade Fung and Miff's tree, our Mushlers offer for them to move in but the two quickly turn out to be unbearable roommates. So when Fung and Miff break their trampoline, our friends decide it's time for them to go back to their homes. But first they need to get rid of the ants.

title: Racer Seven
description: As the ninja prepare for the brutal Speedway Five-Billion race, Lloyd meets a race driver named Seven, who is programmed to lose, but who may hold the key to victory.

title: A trabajar
description: Chitara es el ser vivo más rápido del universo, ihasta que Mandrilok le gana en una carrera! Ahora Chitara tiene que encontrar otra cosa en la cual ser la mejor, imientras el resto de los Thundercats descubren cómo Mandrilok se volvió tan increíblemente rápido!

title: The Chupaca-bro
description: Team Tennyson discovers that a small village's goats are being terrorized by the legendary Chupacabra, but when Ben realizes it's actually Dr. Animo, our hero must thwart the dastardly doctor before he uses the essence of the goats to power up into an unstoppable form!

title: K.O. vs Fink
description: When Fink taunts KO for being a momma's boy, he grapples with newfound insecurity about it.

title: Dizzy
description: M and R help Pops get over his fear of public speaking.

title: Introducing Kevin 11
description: At a local swap meet, Ben instead sets his sights on a Sumo Slammer collectible, but when Kevin takes it for himself, our hero must get it back by overcoming Kevin's secret weapon: an 11th alien!

title: Drawn to Ancestry
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Asian-American Pacific Islander Heritage Month and recognizing amazing kids who learn from their elders to pave their future! We're honoring the special bond between kids and their grandparents as they are Drawn To Ancestry.

title: La traicion
description: Tigro se siente poco apreciado por los demás Thundercats...i¿y por eso empieza a pasar tiempo con Mumm-Ra y a limpiar su Pirámide Negra?!

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Simon por siempre
description: Duncan y Leshawna tratan de aprovecharse del amor de Izzy por el juego de Simón Dice.

title: Numbskull
description: A head Injury turns Mr. Gus into a bumbling fools whose wacky antics make him Uncle Grandpa's coolest friend. No longer the focus of Uncle Grandpa's attention, a jealous Pizza Steve tries to desperately to get back normal. Mr. Gus has to restore social balance in the RV.

title: Sleeper Sofa
description: When the Sky Pirates infiltrate Sheriff HQ, they put our heroes in danger!

title: Dawn of the Donut
description: Dr. Fox's plans to deliver donuts all over the Unikingdom are sidetracked by Unikitty's reluctance to follow instructions.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Eye Spy
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, are traveling on the back of a truck from Montana to Utah. Charlie wants to play a game of Eye Spy. He finds more and more obvious objects for Frank to spy but Frank isn't quite getting the hang of it. Yet!

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: Presumir en el Concurso
description: Cuando Bao Bao regresa y el rey lo convierte en su mascota, Mao Mao debe rescatar a su antiguo compañero.

title: Driving Miss Crazy
description: Duncan leads Beth to believe she's broken his battery-powered bike and makes her chauffeur him around in a wagon for the day as punishment.

title: Maiz Peleas
description: El equipo Tennyson descubre una reconstrucción del conflicto familiar Hartfield-McJoy en el maizal de al lado, pero cuando Hex resucita a los fantasmas de las verdaderas familias enemistadas, Ben debe encontrar la manera de reunirlos si quiere salvar a todos.

title: Crisis at Elder Rock
description: Tragedy strikes the Creek when the Elders get trapped under Elder Rock, and it's up to Craig, Kelsey and JP to rescue them.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Miss Juneteenth
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Freezer Burn
description: Batman and Firestorm team up to fight their respective cold villains, Mr. Freeze and Killer Frost. Complications arise when Firestorm's infatuation for the wily Ms. Frost gets the best of him.

title: El Ladron de Musica
description: Manzana y Cebollín tienen que defender la tienda de música del robo de instrumentos para conseguir una llave de la tienda.

title: Shower Party
description: Things get out of hand when Andrew W. K. helps Pizza Steve and Mr. Gus throw a party while Uncle Grandpa is in the shower.

title: The Lepre-Con
description: On a St. Patrick's Day trip to Ireland, Uncle Grandpa and the gang cross paths with a sneaky leprechaun.

title: Fishing Trip
description: Mel learns that Chad has never taken Clarence fishing, a tradition he sees as a rite of passage, and decides to remedy this with a bonding trip for all the boys! Split into two groups, Mel and Clarence learn a bit about each other while Chad struggles with the ins and outs of fishing.

title: El secreto en la botella
description: Craig necesita compartir un secreto con alguien, por lo que visita al Guardián de los Secretos en el Arroyo.
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Luthor in Paradise
description: With the aid of Circe the Witch, Luthor travels to Paradise Island to steal an artifact that will give him god-like powers. When Superman and Batman arrive on the island to bring him back, they find that they're almost as popular with the Amazons as Luthor on this woman-only island.

title: Falafel en la Carcel
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben sacar a Falafel de la cárcel por un delito que no cometió.

title: #CruzControl
description: Working toward her dream of making her school a better place, Jessica runs for class president. However, when her opponent, the corrupt Oswald Cobblepot, pulls ahead in the race using less-than-honest means, Jessica finds herself compromising the integrity of her honest campaign to beat him!

title: Caillou Tries Karate/Just Like Daddy/Caillou's Safari/Cowboy Caillou
description: Leo comes over to play at Caillou's house./Daddy has a list of things to do around the house./Caillou wants to play with his animal cards but they have disappeared./Jonas, a friend of Dad's and a real cowboy, has invited the family to visit his ranch.

title: Bismuth Casual
description: Pearl invites Bismuth to the roller rink for a lesson on how to forge human relationships.

title: El dia del hamster
description: Owen toma el trabajo de cuidar al hamster de la clase y descubre que es malvado.

title: La Mosca
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben deshacerse de una mosca que se metió en su apartamento o enfrentarse al desalojo.

title: Belson's Backpack
description: After an accidental backpack swap, Clarence discovers that Belson is hiding an artistic side and attempts to foster Belson's creativity.

title: Spice Game
description: Tired of Robin's bland cooking, the other Titans try their hand at spicing up their food.

title: Which Watch
description: After a battle with Kevin gets mysteriously cut short, Ben turns his attention to one upping Gwen at Space Camp. But, when his arch-nemesis, Kevin, returns with his sights strangely set on his cousin, our hero must uncover who is really behind it all, Charmcaster!

title: Unikitty and the Ice Pop Factory
description: An eccentric figure announces a contest to tour her marvelous ice pop factory, sending the gang on a frantic quest to find the winning popsicle stick.

title: The Fog
description: A new villain arrives in Townsville and gives the old villains an enticing offer.

title: Rage of the Red Lanterns
description: Chased by the Red Lanterns, Lobo seeks sanctuary with the Justice League. As the League attempts to stave off the Red Lanterns, Lobo reveals the real reason he wants shelter in the Watchtower, he wants access to a powerful space weapon being held by our heroes.

title: El Chupacabro
description: El equipo Tennyson descubre que las cabras de una pequeña aldea están siendo aterrorizadas por el legendario Chupacabra. Pero cuando Ben se da cuenta de que en realidad se trata del Dr. Ánimo, nuestro héroe debe frustrar al malvado médico.

title: Meet Panthro
description: Panthro may be the strongest cat on Third Earth, but one of his biggest strengths is that he can fix anything!  And the rest of the Thundercats break enough stuff to really put his skills to the test, but it's nothing a pro like Panthro can't handle.

title: Simons Are Forever
description: Duncan and Leshawna try to take advantage of Izzy's love for the game of Simon Says.

title: Carrie
description: Darwin sets out to find a photo of Carrie for the cover of the school yearbook - but they end up reminiscing about all their past spooky shenanigans. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: The Sparkle Solution
description: When Craig is having trouble with some math homework, Sparkle Cadet comes to the rescue.

title: Capture the Flag
description: Water balloon fights, warring factions and the risk of jail time, everything is on the line when Clarence and friends play the biggest game of capture the flag yet! Everyone wants to take home the crown, and the power to control the neighborhood's juice boxes.

title: A Change of Face
description: In Salem Massachusetts, Ben, Gwen and Max once again go up against Charmcaster, whose goal is to switch souls with Ben and possess the Omnitrix. However, Charmcaster first accidentally switches identities with Gwen, and then as spells fly back and forth, Ben and Gwen even end up in one another's bodies before they team up to get rid of Charmcaster once and for all.

title: #SmallVictories
description: A malfunctioning device shrinks Karen into the Microverse, leaving technophobic Diana as her only hope.

title: Crowbar Jones: Origins
description: Grizz pitches his Crowbar Jones prequel film to Nom Nom, hoping Nom Nom will agree to appear in the movie.

title: Baby Bear Genius
description: Ice Bear receives an invitation to attend a prestigious school for baby geniuses… but Grizz and Panda do not.

title: The Glitch
description: In order to stop Unagami the ninja must obtain three Key-tanas, the first of which is hidden in the game zone Terra Kerana, one of Prime Empire's most dangerous game environments.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Rivals
description: From Trigon to Terra to Darkseid, Robin counts down the worst of the worst: the greatest villains to ever challenge the Teen Titans!

title: T.G.I.S
description: The Secret Saturdays come to Bellwood to investigate a rash of chupacabra attacks.

title: Manzallin
description: Manzana y Cebollín quieren llevarse el crédito de haber creado una nueva moda de baile.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Intergalactic Games
description: Super Hero High is facing off against Korugar Academy in the Intergalactic Games, but Lena Luthor takes advantage of the gathering of supers to enact her villainous plan.

title: Paper Pete
description: The pages of the books in the Ooo library turn to Finn and Jake for help before the evil Moldari destroy them.

title: The Badge of Courage
description: When Dibble dresses up as a superhero complete with a pretend belly badge, the Whiffles think she's the real thing and need her to confront an imaginary monster that they believe lives in a cave. She bravely enters the cave but loses her courage when she loses the belly badge, until Funshine convinces her that her bravery came from inside her.

title: I Am Ice Bear
description: After Ice Bear hits his head, Grizz and Panda notice him acting like a different person.

title: La Falla
description: Para detener a Unagami, los Ninjas debe obtener 3 Keytanas, la primera está escondida en Tierra Karana, uno de los entornos de juego más peligrosos.

title: El Kabong's Kabong is Gone
description: When El Kabong's guitar breaks, he must find a new instrument of justice.

title: The Storm
description: Love is in the air and Gumball is caught in the center of an emotional hurricane - literally!

title: The Spoon
description: A crash landing sends Townsville over the edge.

title: The Egg
description: To impress the mother of Anais' playdate, Nicole forces her family to get classy. Nicole arranges a playdate for Anais with the son of a classy lady she met at the supermarket. She hopes that socializing with the right sort of people will help her children climb Elmore's social ladder. The Wattersons try to impress, but ultimately cannot help revealing their true natures. The grown-ups become convinced they want nothing more to do with each other, just as Anais and her playdate discover how much they have in common.

title: Bug City Sleuths
description: To survive in a city inhabited by bugs, the Bears become noir-style detectives.

title: El Laberinto del Dragon Rojo
description: Aún en la zona de juego de Tierra Karana, Okino tiene que elegir entre ayudar a sus aliados ninjas, u obedecer las órdenes de su Maestro, Unagami.

title: Lion 4: Alternate Ending
description: Lion coughs up a magical key, and Steven goes on a quest to find what it unlocks.

title: Boot Castle/Avocado's Long Time Out/Tanks Giving
description: Findley discovers a boot that him and Lucas use as a castle./ When they hear Avocado has been put in her naughty crate, Lucas and Findley entertain her./ Lucas brings Dimples things from around the house so she doesn't feel left out.

title: Imaginary Fiend/Cootie Gras
description: Imaginary Fiend: The new boy in school has a special friend nobody else can see. When this imaginary friend begins destroying the class, the girls must imagine how to stop him./Cootie Gras: Mojo observes that everyone is staying away from little Harry Pitt because he has cooties. So Mojo concocts a plan to keep the girls away by using this cootie-covered boy as bait.

title: The Maze of the Red Dragon
description: Still in the game zone Terra Kerana, the Samurai guide Okino has to choose between helping his allies the ninja, or obeying the evil orders of his Master, Unagami.

title: The Gold Standard
description: It's St. Patrick's Day and after wishing to become a leprechaun, Beast Boy becomes obsessed with gold.

title: Trading Day
description: After Craig accidentally destroys a shipment of rare Chocorolls at the Trading Tree, Kit makes him work off his debt by running her trades throughout the Creek!

title: Bakugan Battle League, Tokyo Edition/Battle Royal
description: Bakugan Battle League, Tokyo Edition: It's the start of the Bakugan Battle League - Toyko edition! The first round will be a Battle Royale style competition, where only half the competitors will make it through to the next round. Along with the Awesome brawlers the field of competitors is filled with familiar friends and foes./Battle Royal: The first round of the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo edition continues. The Awesome Brawler's and their Bakugan battle their way through the challenge and face off against tough competitors.

title: Mao Mao's Nakey
description: When MM loses his clothes while trying to scale the Ruby Pure Heart, he has to get back to Sheriff's HQ by daybreak.

title: Los Acantilados de la Histeria
description: Los Ninjas suben a los Acantilados de la histeria y descubren que Unagami convierte a los jugadores en cubos de energía para construir un portal.

title: Croissant
description: A giant cocoon mysteriously appears in the Titans' living room, and no one can find Beast Boy.

title: #DetentionClub
description: Five socially disparate teens, Hal, Pam, Kara, Zee and Garth, find they have more in common than they thought after spending a Saturday in detention.

title: Stop! Hamster Time
description: Owen takes over the job of caring for the class hamster and learns that he's evil.

title: The New Frontier
description: When Jake has a dream that predicts when his last days are, Finn intervenes when the events of the dream start to actually happen.

title: Bad Heir Day
description: Princess Zange's Autostyle Magisword is stolen and it's up to the Warriors to retrieve it so their royal leader can face her subjects without bad hair.

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

title: Dia de trueque
description: Cuando, por accidente, Craig destruye un cargamento de chocolates poco comunes en el árbol del trueque, Kit lo hace trabajar para pagar su deuda: idebe ocuparse de los intercambios de Kit por todo el bosque!
originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

title: Room for Ruby
description: Steven's Gem family continues to grow.

title: Drawn to Community
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating awesome kids who are giving back and making a difference to those around them. CN is recognizing extraordinary girls who are channeling their interests into outreach as they are Drawn to… Community!

title: Plastic Man Saves the World
description: Plastic Man feels shuffled off to the side as the Justice League battles Brainiac so he takes it upon himself to infiltrate the alien's ship on his own and thwart the villain's plans.

title: Dia de limpieza
description: Victor y Valentino adquieren un nuevo respeto por la limpieza después de que la casa de Chata los atrapa dentro de su laberinto de paredes antiguas y mágicas.

title: Monster Weather
description: Max takes the kids to a drought stricken Chicago to see his favorite golden oldie band perform at a huge music festival. Once there, our heroes cross paths with a deranged weatherman.

title: Dr. Dometome
description: Lion-O is tasked with mapping the beaches of Third Earth, which leads to him somehow draining the oceans of all water entirely. Woops! But a mysterious scientist with a robotic frog says they can fix everything by traveling under the earth, which is just the kinda crazy adventure Lion-O is all about!

title: Mandora - The Evil Chaser
description: Lion-O "accidentally" releases a whole space prison-full of space criminals and winds up on the wrong side of the law. On the right side of the law is Mandora the Evil Chaser, a no nonsense space cop! Lion-O's gonna have to work real hard to prove he's not a criminal, just a little bit of an oaf!
